{"tid":1561244,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"警棍無鋒，大巧不工，九月前持之橫行天下。","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:02:05.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4350a43d929f549ae9b42f1da847b11d369a0f5e","tid":1561244,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"胡椒噴霧，無堅不摧，七月前以之與警總義士爭鋒。<br />\n<br />\n過期催淚彈，八月前所用，誤傷市民不祥，悔恨無已，乃棄之深谷。<br />\n<br />\n警棍無鋒，大巧不工，九月前持之橫行天下。<br />\n<br />\n十一國慶後，不滯於物，草木竹石均可攻擊示威者。自此精修，漸進於無劍勝有劍之境。"},{"pid":"c8c65e07a01e04e4fa189fdc251c5ae4db66c8a0","tid":1561244,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d5efdeb65663b9973970404bb10be054fa1c361f","tid":1561244,"uid":15880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"幾時教連登仔破共式"},{"pid":"953b5f8c8aad6b9b9a8bd64aeb6cb1694290c72c","tid":1561244,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">九月十五，港島見！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\